Rubric (hard constraints gate the design):
- power_budget [hard]: sum(active_power_W) <= 12
- peak_power [hard]: sum(peak_power_W per rail) <= rail_current_A * rail_V
- voltage_rails [hard]: every input voltage is supplied by a rail
- connectors [hard]: every connector has a mating pair
- power_margin [soft]: active power leaves headroom
- endurance [hard]: battery_Wh / avg_power_W >= 0.75
- compute [hard]: accelerator TOPS >= 21
- sensing [hard]: camera meets resolution/fps and CSI lanes fit
- comms [hard]: radios+antennas cover ['5GHz', 'UWB']
- thermal [hard]: all parts rated across [-20, 60] C
- environment [hard]: enclosure IP >= IP67
- mass_budget [hard]: sum(mass_g) <= 450
- size_enclosure [hard]: all boards fit the enclosure
- cost [soft]: minimize BOM cost
- lead_time [soft]: minimize lead time

